      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented here is an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine, smoke-free interior that reflects a history of fastidious care. Mechanically flawless and visually striking, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. We invite you to experience this peerless offering firsthand.",
