    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel inside. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and fall in love with it just like I did!",
