    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in a climate-controlled environment and presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'day-one' state; the premium leather retains its original scent and supple texture, and every surface\u2014from the dashboard to the door cards\u2014is completely devoid of wear or sun damage. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It drives with the precision and smoothness of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine, investment-grade example that has been pampered with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy.",
