      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You\u2019ve got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is seriously in absolute mint condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it still looks and drives just like it did when it first left the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
